---
// About and contact section with structured data for local business
---

<section
  class="relative py-32 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[800px]"
  data-purpose="about-contact"
  id="hikayemiz"
>
  <!-- Parallax Background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <img
      alt="Zeynep Ticaret mağaza iç mekanı ve ürün sergileme"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCCrP21jlsxphGu-U_komNxxawz44W27j9cH3ObZcw5_QoGvbcmhQ8heveBxm9jPdSAhbr83RtYKdOy1VBUsQ8wBcqziMJiGpFJKUqINwqrFg2MbfWmJFILtAcCHSxewFzqV23jA5-XY6UTqpppnePkuF_8SNGTR5IDWeGKuV8NKUpnR2C1pJmvf2CF63d7rG32rcZ0Wwd8uk6SaZj9Sjz8Fjy43OProaR_6VydBvqP4z9ZS8DctkRIHO7Q-4N4QVPBqIYIZetrC7Q"
      width="1200"
      height="800"
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-stone-900/30"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Glassmorphism Card -->
  <div
    class="relative z-10 w-[95%] max-w-5xl glass-card rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl flex flex-col md:flex-row reveal-observer"
    id="iletisim"
  >
    <!-- Left: Story -->
    <div class="p-8 lg:p-12 md:w-3/5 border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-stone-200">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl mb-8">Bizim Hikayemiz</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Denizli'nin kalbinde başlayan yolculuğumuz, yerel butik anlayışını modern ev
          dekorasyonuyla buluşturmak üzere doğdu. <strong class="text-stone-900"
            >Zeynep Ticaret</strong
          > olarak, sadece eşya satmıyor, yaşam alanlarınıza kimlik katacak parçaları özenle
          seçiyoruz.
        </p>
        <p>
          Geleneksel ticaretin samimiyetini dijital dünyanın hızıyla birleştirerek, ikas
          altyapılı mağazamız üzerinden Türkiye'nin her noktasına mutluluk ulaştırıyoruz.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 flex gap-4 grayscale opacity-70 hover:grayscale-0 hover:opacity-100 transition-all">
        <!-- Brand Badge -->
        <div
          class="px-4 py-2 bg-stone-100 rounded font-bold text-xs tracking-tighter uppercase"
        >
          ikas Official Partner
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Contact -->
    <div class="p-8 lg:p-12 md:w-2/5 flex flex-col justify-between bg-stone-50/50">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl mb-8">Bize Ulaşın</h2>
        <address class="space-y-6 not-italic">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-1">Adres</p>
            <p class="text-stone-900 font-medium italic">
              Denizli Butik Mağazası, Merkez Efendi, Denizli
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-stone-400 mb-1">Telefon</p>
            <a
              href="tel:+905383045524"
              class="text-stone-900 font-medium hover:text-stone-700 transition-colors"
            >
              0538 304 55 24
            </a>
          </div>
        </address>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 space-y-4">
        <a
          class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 w-full bg-[#25D366] text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all"
          href="https://wa.me/905383045524"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          title="WhatsApp ile iletişim kurun"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-6 h-6 fill-current"
            viewbox="0 0 24 24"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              d="M.057 24l1.687-6.163c-1.041-1.804-1.588-3.849-1.587-5.946.003-6.556 5.338-11.891 11.893-11.891 3.181.001 6.167 1.24 8.413 3.488 2.246 2.248 3.484 5.232 3.484 8.412-.003 6.557-5.338 11.892-11.893 11.892-1.997-.001-3.951-.5-5.688-1.448l-6.309 1.656zm6.29-4.464c1.562.928 3.177 1.397 4.96 1.398 5.403 0 9.8-4.398 9.802-9.8.001-2.618-1.02-5.08-2.876-6.937-1.856-1.857-4.319-2.877-6.94-2.877-5.405 0-9.802 4.398-9.804 9.8.001 1.838.513 3.635 1.478 5.198l-1.008 3.688 3.771-.989z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          WhatsApp ile Sorun
        </a>
        <p class="text-[10px] text-center text-stone-400 uppercase tracking-widest">
          Çalışma Saatleri: 09:00 - 19:00
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
